35 receipt of the request and the copy of the bill or resolution, the Fiscal Research Division shall
36 prepare the fiscal note as promptly as possible. The Fiscal Research Division shall prepare the
37 fiscal note and transmit it to the sponsor within two weeks after the request is made, unless the
38 sponsor agrees to an extension of time.
39 This fiscal note shall be attached to the original of each proposed bill or resolution that is
