12 SECTION 3.(a) G.S. 160D-108.1 reads as rewritten:
13 "§ 160D-108.1. Vested rights – site-specific vesting plans.
14 …
15 (c) Approval and Amendment of Plans. – If a site-specific vesting plan is based on an
