30 (2) The landowner of the property subject to a rezoning petition or the applicant
31 for a text amendment is a person with whom the member has a close familial,
32 business, or other associational relationship.
33 (3) The member has a fixed opinion prior to the hearing on the matter that is not
34 susceptible to change.
35 (4) The member has undisclosed ex parte communication about the matter.
36 …."
